lead_paragraph: Jimmy Walker shrugged off some recent struggles to shoot a five-under-par 65 and claim the first-round lead in the PGA Championship at a hot, steamy Baltusrol Golf Club on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Walker Sets First-Round PGA Pace With Sixty Five, Stenson Two Back
